# repcode3_phaseflip — [[3,1]] phase-flip 반복코드 인코더. stab=X0X1,X1X2. golden=H^⊗3 @ parity. QEC stabilizer 인코더(qec_family). plan=봉인 h_gate·cnot, no MatrixGate. golden=closed-form parity/Sylvester (Qualtran 비의존 독립경로).
